text: Aslı Karataş (born July 20, 1990) is a Turkish women's football midfielder currently playing in the Turkish Women's First Football League for Konak Belediyespor in Izmir with jersey number 35. She was a member of the Turkey girls' U-17 and Turkey women's U-19 teams. ==Early life== Aslı Karataş was born in Konak, Izmir on July 20, 1990. ==Playing career== ===Club=== She obtained her license for Elitspor in her hometown on February 7, 2003. After capping once only, she moved to Konak Belediyespor for the 2008–09 season. She debuted at the 2015–16 UEFA Women's Champions League qualifying round match against the Albanian team KF Vllaznia Shkodër on August 13, 2015. ===International=== Karataş appeared in one match of the Turkey girls' U-17 team in 2006.
